* The full `RingEquiv` form `R 4 ≃+* Mat₂(ℂ)` is **not type-correct**
  (cardinality mismatch); the correct upgrade is the `F₂`-subring iso
  (option a) plus the `ℂ`-basis content (option b) delivered here.

